      <description>I did a quick & dirty patch : on modules/prepare.php
<code>
 --- 1 
+++ 2 
@@ -35,6 +35,12 @@
 $img = eZContentObjectAttribute::fetch( $NodeId, $Version )->attribute('content');&#13;
 $image_path = $img-&gt;attributeFromOriginal('url');&#13;
 $absolute_image_path = eZSys::rootDir() . "/" . $image_path;&#13;
+&#13;
+if ( !file_exists( $absolute_image_path ) )&#13;
+        {&#13;
+            $sourceFileHandler = eZClusterFileHandler::instance( $img-&gt;attributeFromOriginal('url'));&#13;
+            $sourceFileHandler-&gt;fetch();&#13;
+        }&#13;
 &#13;
 // TODO: Check for editing rights&#13;
&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
 and then it works</description>
